name: Silver Golden Goddess
description:
ALL PIECES ARE HANDMADE AND ONE OF A KIND, NO TWO ALIKE 

This is one of my favorite pieces, it is made up of silver and gold toned brass pieces, with amethyst, and a beautiful centerpiece. 
It is a body jewelry piece meaning it goes on and adorns your whole body, even your back! it is definitely a conversational piece and you won't get tired of wearing it, with jeans and a t-shirt, or with your fanciest gown
